Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.20,0:00:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.20,0:00:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not done talking yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.12,0:00:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we are. I'll never see you guys again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Hurry up and catch Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.26,0:00:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.81,0:00:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can they be that strong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.41,0:00:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.41,0:00:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are CP9.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.83,0:00:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a world-class top secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.04,0:00:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a matter that people\Nlike you can get involved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.96,0:01:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time for the igniters\Nto go off. We have to hurry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.59,0:01:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a rare occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.30,0:01:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show you something\Ninteresting before we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.37,0:01:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Devil Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucci... What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.18,0:01:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Cat-Cat Fruit...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.89,0:01:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leopard Model...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A leopard human...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.86,0:02:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that appearance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:18.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:21.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:24.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:33.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:43.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:50.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.99,0:02:57.94,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.96,0:03:05.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:08.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:12.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:16.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:19.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:23.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:27.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:30.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:34.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:38.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:41.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:44.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:50.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:58.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:08.06,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"The Straw Hat Pirates Annihilated?\NThe Menace of the Leopard Model!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...! Is this the pirates' doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must still be a lot of people left inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Iceberg-san?!\NWhat's going on upstairs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go check!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! The rest of you, put out the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the fire has started to spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if you're a\Nleopard human or what, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:05:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I won't let you lay a finger on Iceberg-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Carnivore Zoan types\Nbecome more brutal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Logia types,\NZoan types, and Paramythia types...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many unique powers exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genuine physical augmentation\Nis the trait of Zoan types.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.27,0:05:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more we train, the stronger we get.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Zoan type is the strongest species\Nwhen it comes to a close attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna hear stuff\Nabout monsters like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want to waste time, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since we have to take care of you guys\Nbefore we get wrapped up in flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foremen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucci... the craftsmen are coming upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. They can't make it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:06:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tempest Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back! The ceiling is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paulie, what're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking you out of this place no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not possible! Your injuries\Nare too severe! How can you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Paulie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call my name... as if we're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get... out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it have to be you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I considered you guys my friends all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pigeon jerk...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finger Pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:08:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a nice flight off the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:09:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.70,0:09:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma! Grandma! There's a big fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:10:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Galley-La's main office.\NWhat a terrible thing to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A terrible thing? Did someone set the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but often, a bad feeling turns out to be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Iceberg is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, this is all because of\Nthat thing. It just shouldn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What pirates say cannot be evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This incident will now be shrouded in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san... No matter how good\Nof a shipbuilding engineer you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or even if you're the mayor of a big city...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you, a mere citizen, shouldn't have disobeyed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the powerful World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go. We'll find Tom's\Nother disciple Franky--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,rather, Cutty Flam, and take\Nthe blueprints from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get everyone out of the building?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.80,0:11:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go inside anymore!\NHave each team account for its men!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Iceberg-san? Did you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.68,0:11:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he's still in this fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three of our foremen are with him.\NThere's no way he got left in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys go check around there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.86,0:11:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's one of the Straw Hats. There's no mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she jump out a window?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:12:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was probably surrounded by\Nflames and had trouble escaping.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... what a terrible thing they've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make her tell us where the others are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll capture all of them and\Nhand them over to the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blueno... So Franky was at your bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he rushed out to find Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like he doesn't stay in one place for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But people with bad timing really exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got Long-nose with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want him to sing in the key of C...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! That's not it! How many\Ntimes do I have to tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's "If you don't want him to sink in the sea"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the key of C...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:12:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"In the sea"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what were you listening to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's important is to get the\Nmessage to Straw Hat, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're saying that message ain't gonna work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro is gonna beat you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say it like, "If you don't\Nwant him to sink in the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,come to the warehouse under the bridge!\NFranky sends his regards!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind you, even if he comes, Bro is\Ngonna beat the crap out of him, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did you say is waiting for whom where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're busy right now! Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't wanna die,\Nanswer my question in three seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's talking nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what family we're in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which place do you mean by\Nthe warehouse under the bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky is there, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What business do you have with Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.99,0:14:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna talk to him, then talk to us first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you left the friends\Nyou traveled together with
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all the way from the East Blue, for the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.31,0:14:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys crying for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy! We're not crying, you dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.11,0:14:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true that I was moved by your\Nprotecting this ship all by yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while all those things were happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not crying! None of us are crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is their problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, now you know that those guys\Nand I are no longer friends, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sing about your hardships!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The song title is, "Severed Friendship!\NNorthern Wind Chop!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making fun of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is the tea ready yet? I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We'll bring it right over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exhausted from crying...\NNot that I cried, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Bro. It's a little hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I get it, brother, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch, it's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Settle down a little, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.18,0:15:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you take a break\Nand have some tea, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't blame you. You must be\Nholding quite a grudge against us
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for taking 200 million Berries\Naway from you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since it led to such a big fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was meant to happen, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding a grudge doesn't do me any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That 200 million...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used it all, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to knock you over?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now... Don't get so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've shown me how manly you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, now I have to calm my anger\Nover the complete destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the Franky House, which was\Nmy home and demolition factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, you guys\Nannihilated my subordinates!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you bastards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bro!\N--The anger welled up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, brother, although a lot happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's calm our anger towards\Neach other on this matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and settle it as "Heave-ho! Heave-ho!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean "fifty-fifty."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean "fifty-fifty," Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna do now that you're alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have nowhere to go anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, I can\Ntake you in. Work for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I don't wanna\Nbecome a demolition worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I left my group, I'm still a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen to my song.\NIt's titled "The Pirate Code."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, are you making fun of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... I'm trying to think what\Nyou should do next, for your sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:17:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, is it okay for you\Nto relax in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A storm surge is coming soon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's exactly why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Aqua Laguna comes,\Nwe all have to help each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now until late into the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,houses will be submerged\Nup to the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.92,0:18:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're in the backstreets or capes at\Na time like this, you don't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry if\Nyou keep your ship here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Thanks... I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy! Don't act like we're strangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, it must be tough to have\Nflood damage like that every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, everyone's used to this\Nannual evacuation, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more problematic
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is that the water level of the sea\Nhas been increasing every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The backstreet area you can see above\Nthe sea now is a town built on the rooftops
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of an old town that existed\Nseveral hundred years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that the shipbuilding\Nisland and the backstreets
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were completely on one land a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.96,0:19:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, so much of the area is under\Nwater that it's called a floating city.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.22,0:19:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the sidewalks became canals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Properly speaking, rather than saying\Nthat the water level is increasing,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they say that the foundation\Nof the island is sinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As it stands, the areas in town we can\Nlive in will get smaller and smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Even this pretty floating\Ncity has hardships too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, well, if push comes to shove,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can take the sea train\Nand go live somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that... now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was only a bit over a decade\Nago that the sea train was created.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that time, it wasn't quite\Nthat easy to go across the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, people were rarely able to\Ngo back and forth between the islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On this isolated island,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.89,0:19:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the residents vaguely imagined\Ntheir land being submerged someday
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.52,0:20:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and grew completely hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What relieved people's\Nworries even about the future
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was the sea train, Puffing Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can now go across the sea\Nwhenever you want without a Log Pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this was big progress!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea train really is an incredible thing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water Seven came back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to a great shipwright\Nnamed Tom who created the sea train.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.98,0:20:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were all saved by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say hello to "Bro" for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We now know the location.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.74,0:22:19.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a dream that day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.33,0:22:24.14,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Our belief in ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.16,0:22:32.16,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,makes us able to cross the wildly surging ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.30,0:22:41.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You're braver and more caring than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.85,0:22:50.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever depart this ship\Nand live in a different world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.03,0:23:01.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we can all surely smile
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.59,0:23:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Long-nose. What're you\Ngonna do after you fix that ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.80,0:23:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What else? I'll go on an\Nadventure with her again and...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.47,0:23:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible. You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.55,0:23:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What'd you say?!\N--That ship can't even reach\Nthe next island anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.97,0:23:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you demolish that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.14,0:23:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.06,0:23:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.02,0:23:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Man Who Is Loved Even\Nby His Ship! Usopp's Tears!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.15,0:23:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
